18768326.Line7.136591: Here is how we’ll do this: show this insignia to the guard. Tell them you have an urgent message for their commander.

3194C0F2.Line12.136591: Once you're in, hold their attention. Distract them however you can. I’ll be right on your heels.

3FF2D964.Line5.136591: He's an Inquisitor captain. A real zealot, can’t be reasoned with. I’ve tried.

68ACAEF3.VoiceDir7.136591: Explaining a detailed plan to the player so nothing is missed.

8EEB85E0.Line1.136591: Damn it. This is Osric’s doing. The bastard has been stalking my every move.
